Title: Impermanence
---
The day is ending and our life is one day shorter. Let us look carefully at
what we have done. Let us practice diligently, putting our whole heart into
the path of meditation. Let us live deeply each moment and in freedom, so
the time doesnâ€™t slip away meaninglessly.
